These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, dressmaker
There are 2 different nationalities: pakistani, canadian
1. the dressmaker is somewhere to the left of the pakistani##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Job           | dressmaker | designer |
| Nationality   | canadian     | pakistani  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
2 different pets are kept: goat, lizard
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daffodil, azalea
1. the person who growsdaffodil is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Pet         | lizard   | goat      |
| Flower   | daffodil | azalea |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, alhambra
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, subway
1. the bongani-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| Cigar   | alhambra | bongani    |
| Transport     | boat | subway |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-4::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, zombie
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, september
1. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the right of the person watching musical movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical   | zombie |
| Birthday   | march | september |

 #################################

 
